                "title": "临事场域"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">融化</span>：本伤害<span>+2</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">超导</span>：本伤害<span>+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害<span>+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_2393552109524427245.png",
